When using Poppler 0.17.0, I needed to swap the blue and red channels,
otherwise the colors (other than black and white) looked weird.

From upstream:
http://trac.emma-soft.com/epdfview/changeset/367

Index: src/PDFDocument.cxx
===================================================================
--- a/src/PDFDocument.cxx
+++ b/src/PDFDocument.cxx
@@ -21,4 +21,5 @@
